column16: Aaron Hill lines out to second baseman Anthony Rendon.
Welington Castillo hit by pitch.    Paul Goldschmidt to 2nd.
Paul Goldschmidt grounds into a force out, third baseman Yunel Escobar to second baseman Anthony Rendon.   Ender Inciarte scores.    A.  J.   Pollock out at 2nd.    Paul Goldschmidt to 1st.
